<!--
VOICING PLAN:
- Key C, 4/4. Processional hymn with broad half-note voicings.
- Non-diatonic Eb, F#, Bb treated: Eb as bIII (flat-③m label), others as passing.
- CΔ7 color kept (bar 5), Dm7 bass line at bar 2.
- LH "33" root pos throughout; RH light thirds/fourths.

VOICE LEADING HIGHLIGHTS:
- LH stepwise C→D→C→F→G→F→E→D→C descent over 8 bars.
- Bridge bars 9-12 chromatic color: Am, A7, Gm, G→Em.

TEXTURE ARC:
- Full opening; breathing space bar 4 (G pedal); climax bar 9-12 bridge; resolves to G bar 16.
-->
